            "notes": "The deck focuses on building a strong aggro strategy with Aragorn, King of Gondor as the commander. It includes a mix of low-cost creatures, removal spells, and counterspells to maintain board control and pressure the opponent. The deck also features various utility lands and cantrips to ensure card advantage and consistency. By utilizing efficient spells and powerful creatures, the goal is to quickly overwhelm the opponent and secure victory through aggressive plays and smart decision-making. The deck is designed to be fast-paced and proactive, constantly applying pressure and forcing the opponent to react defensively. With a focus on tempo and efficiency, the deck aims to outmaneuver the opponent and come out on top in one-on-one matches."
